nk" rel="noopener">虚拟产品展示</a>”。与此同时，MoguLive 副主编 Takahiro Horita 将登台。</p><p>该网络研讨会可免费参加，但需提前预订。地点将是Zoom。</p><p> <strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf4y2nZIElGum49K3HlbiYFL_GdIvnnspiLKPLoo0purIlDTQ/viewform">在此申请</a></strong></p><p><a href="https://uyet.jp/vtubernext/">官方网站</a></p><p>（参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000079.000097346.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">新闻稿</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/uyet-mogulive-webinar/">Uyet首席执行官兼MoguLive副主编将举办一场解释“Metaverse x VTuber”的网络研讨会的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; 
